criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. at least 3-year working experience as a psychiatrist;

          2. provide outpatient services for at least 1 year with the frequency of more than once a
             week;

          3. willingness to receive standardized electronic interventions on BZDs and Z-drugs
             prescription.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. will retire within six months;

          2. refuse to extract their prescription information from the outpatient database.
